    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s a total stunner\u2014it\u2019s like she just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, so it\u2019s in truly incredible shape inside and out. No scratches, no smells, just pure perfection. I'm looking for a great new home for this beauty, so come check it out and see for yourself. You definitely won\u2019t be disappointed!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
