      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 26
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade 1994 Mazda RX-7 FD, preserved in museum-quality condition. The heart of this machine is the 13B-REW rotary powerplant, featuring a factory-spec sequential twin-turbocharger system that delivers a linear power band with seamless transition. Recent compression testing shows exceptional results across all rotor faces, confirming the integrity of the apex seals. The chassis remains a masterclass in engineering, utilizing a front-midship engine placement for a perfect 50/50 weight distribution. Every suspension component, including the lightweight aluminum double-wishbones and factory-spec dampers, is in pristine order. The Torsen limited-slip differential remains tight, and the 5-speed manual transmission provides crisp, short-throw engagement. With zero vacuum leaks and an immaculate undercarriage, this FD represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM performance engineering.",
      "price": 46500.0,
